            <documentation>
                <html>
                    <![CDATA[
                        <div style="margin-top:8px;background-color:#eee;padding:8px;">
                        <p>EXAMPLE SCRIPT: Create a new image layer from a file on the desktop named New.png and set the new layer's preserve transparency to true and constrain proportions to false:</p>
                        <p style="font-family:Verdana,sans-serif;padding-left:6em;text-indent:-4.5em;">
                        <b>tell the front</b> <span style="color:blue;font-style:italic;">document</span> <b>to</b> <span style="color:blue;"><b>make</b></span> <span style="color:blue;">new</span> <span style="color:blue;font-style:italic;">image layer</span> <span style="color:blue;">with properties</span> {<span style="color:blue;font-style:italic;">file</span>:((<span style="color:#0016B0;"><b>path to</b></span> <span style="color:#4415B0;font-style:italic;">desktop</span> <span style="color:#0016B0;">as</span> <span style="color:blue;font-style:italic;">text</span>) & "New.png"), <span style="color:#6C05D3;">preserve transparency</span>:<span style="color:#6C05D3;font-style:italic;">true</span>, <span style="color:#6C05D3;">constrain proportions</span>:<span style="color:#6C05D3;font-style:italic;">false</span>}</p>
                        </div>
                    ]]>
                </html>
            </documentation>
        </class>
