            <documentation>
                <html>
                    <![CDATA[
                        <div style="margin-top:8px;background-color:#eee;padding:8px;">
                        <p>EXAMPLE SCRIPT: Create a new group layer, store the reference to it in a variable and move the last layer in the document the new group layer:</p>
                        <p style="font-family:Verdana,sans-serif;text-indent:1.5em;line-height:0.8em;">
                            <b>tell the front</b> <span style="color:blue;font-style:italic;">document</span>
                        </p>
                        <p style="font-family:Verdana, sans-serif;text-indent:4em;line-height:0.8em;">
                            <b>set</b> <span style="color:#408000;">newGroup</span> <b>to</b> <span style="color:blue;"><b>make</b></span> <span style="color:blue;">new</span> <span style="color:blue;font-style:italic;">group layer</span> <span style="color:blue;">at</span> <b>the front of</b> <span style="color:blue;font-style:italic;">layers</span>
                        </p>
                        <p style="font-family:Verdana, sans-serif;text-indent:4em;line-height:0.8em;">
                            <span style="color:blue;"><b>move</b></span> <b>the last</b> <span style="color:blue;"><i>layer</i> to</span> <b>the front of</b> <span style="color:blue;font-style:italic;">layers</span> <b>of</b> <span style="color:#408000;">newGroup</span>
                        </p>
                        <p style="font-family:Verdana,sans-serif;text-indent:1.5em;line-height:0.8em;">
                            <b>end tell</b>
                        </p>
                        </div>
                    ]]>
